===============================================================================
1. Prerequisites:
===============================================================================

kafka-python is required to run the test app. To install kafka,
run following commands:

  $ pip3 install kafka-python

===============================================================================
2. Purpose:
===============================================================================

This document shall describe about the sample deepstream_kafka_test application.

It is meant for demonstration of how to use the various DeepStream SDK
elements in the pipeline and extract meaningful insights from a video stream using the service-maker API and send these insights directly to a kafka server.

===============================================================================
2. Usage:
===============================================================================

  Run with the h264 elementary stream
    $ python3 deepstream_kafka_test.py <h264_elementary_stream>